    <section id="id17054952">
      <title>Learning Objectives</title>
      <para id="id17054958">With 100% accuracy during a: memory building activity, exercises, lab assignment, problems, or timed quiz/exam; the student is expected to:</para>
      <list id="id17054968" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
        <item>Define the terms on the definitions as listed in the modules associated with this chapter.</item>
        <item>Identify which selection control structures are test after iteration.</item>
        <item>Be able to write pseudo code or flowcharting for the do while control structure.</item>
        <item>Be able to write C++ source code for a do while control structure.</item>
      </list>
    </section>
