      <section id="id17055076">
        <title>Creating a Folder or Sub-Folder for Chapter 13 Files</title>
        <para id="id17055083">Depending on your compiler/IDE, you should decide where to download and store source code files for processing. Prudence dictates that you create these folders as needed prior to downloading source code files. A suggested sub-folder for the <term>Bloodshed Dev-C++ 5 compiler/IDE</term> might be named:</para>
        <list id="id17055107" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Chapter_13 within the folder named: Cpp_Source_Code_Files</item>
        </list>
        <para id="id17055122">If you have not done so, please create the folder(s) and/or sub-folder(s) as appropriate.</para>
      </section>
      <section id="id17055129">
        <title>Download the Lab File(s)</title>
        <para id="id17055135">Download and store the following file(s) to your storage device in the appropriate folder(s). You may need to right click on the link and select "Save Target As" in order to download the file.</para>
