        <para id="id17055179">Read and follow the directions below carefully, and perform the steps in the order listed.</para>
        <list id="id17055185" list-type="bulleted"><item>Create a source code file from the Lab_13_Pseudocode.txt file. Name it: Lab_13.cpp</item>
